    <item>
      <title>Ancient Horse DNA (horses warp regardless of gear)</title>
      <author>aaron31121</author>
      <link>https://gamebanana.com/mods/432466</link>
      <comments>https://gamebanana.com/mods/432466#PostsListModule</comments>
      <guid isPermaLink="false">859d9f03af8472d37847e31800ae467610df6d54</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 15 Oct 2024 16:22:19 +0000</pubDate>
      <description>&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/64128848229bf.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6412884ab29d7.jpg"/&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Update:&lt;/strong&gt; Add Switch BOTW support&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Add .pchtxt file for Switch BOTW.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;br&gt;Well, I got bored of &lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/mods/371538"&gt;riding my horse&lt;/a&gt; through the desert.  From this boredom came crushing despair until I one day realized that &lt;b&gt;my boredom didn't stem from wasting too many hours of my life&lt;/b&gt; playing BOTW!  Rather!  It was because I and my four-legged furry friends&lt;b&gt; lacked sufficient ability to express our tastes properly!&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Like most of you, I and my four-legged friends have been limited to a single choice of horse gear....the Ancient gear.  I mean - after all - who wants to lose the convenience of being able to warp your horse to oneself from anywhere on the map?  But at the same time, the Ancient horse gear looks rather....tacky....to say the least!  How could you do this to us, Nintendo?&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Well, in the end I expanded my very limited reverse engineering skills used to create &lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/mods/371538"&gt;Unauthorized Horse&lt;/a&gt; and they - combined them with a boatload of caffeine (as in, the drug, not the program) and way too many late nights of staring at a wall of PowerPC assembly - finally figured out an ASM patch to make your horse capable of warping to you regardless of gear choice.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;In the end I finally escaped Nintendo's forced-monotony and - erm - somewhat questionable ... style choices.  And so, despite their best efforts to the contrary, my trusty steed and I are back to traveling the land in style!&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Hope you enjoy :-P</description>
      <media:content url="https://files.gamebanana.com/mods/ancienthorsedna_v1_0_2.bnp" type="application/octet-stream"/>
      <media:content url="https://files.gamebanana.com/mods/ancienthorsedna_patches_v1_0_2_hax_94321.zip" type="application/zip"/>
      <media:content url="https://files.gamebanana.com/mods/ancienthorsedna_switch_exefs_patch_v1_0_2.zip" type="application/zip"/>
      <category>Horse</category>
      <category>Mounts</category>
    </item>
