ebanana.com/img/ss/mods/669faf7808171.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/669faf9f40711.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/669fafcc7ba8c.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/669fb002b291a.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/669fb002b8eea.jpg"/&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Update:&lt;/strong&gt; Individual Selection Ver&lt;br&gt;&lt;em&gt;Addition&lt;/em&gt;: Individual Selection Ver&lt;br&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;This mod is created based on NUDELINK 2.0&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://s12.gifyu.com/images/SawnT.gif" width="40%"&gt;&lt;br&gt;Enabled physics on his sword and balls.&lt;br&gt;There are 3 versions.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;[ Standard Ver ]&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;This replaces default armor and Old Shirt + Well-Worn Trousers&lt;br&gt;There are four options.&lt;br&gt;・No Acc&lt;br&gt;Only pubic hair is included without accessories.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;・With Acc&lt;br&gt;Both accessories and pubic hair are included.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;・No Acc Hairless&lt;br&gt;Accessories and pubic hair have been removed.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;・With Acc Hairless&lt;br&gt;Only accessories are included and pubic hair has been removed.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;[ Armor Edit Ver ]&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;This version replaces most of the armor with nude-edited armor.&lt;br&gt;In addition to the same options as the standard version, you can choose your hair color.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;--Armor Edit Ver&amp;nbsp;Replacement list--&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;1: A well-Worn Outfit&amp;nbsp; 2:Stealth Set&amp;nbsp; 3: Gerudo Clothes&amp;nbsp; 4: Climbing Set&amp;nbsp; 5: Desert Voe Set&amp;nbsp; 6: Barbarian Set&amp;nbsp; 7: Sand Boots&amp;nbsp; 8: Snow Boots&amp;nbsp; 9: Champion's Tunic&amp;nbsp; 10: Hero Set&amp;nbsp; 11: Tingle's Set 12:Flamebreaker Set&amp;nbsp; 13: Hylian Set&amp;nbsp; 14: Zora Set&amp;nbsp; 15: Rubber Set&amp;nbsp; 16: Radiant Set&amp;nbsp; 17: Ancient Set&amp;nbsp; 18: Salvager Set&amp;nbsp; 19: Hero Of Wild Set&amp;nbsp; 20: Dark Set&amp;nbsp; 21: Fierce Deity Set 22: Soldier's Set&amp;nbsp; 23: Snowquill Set&amp;nbsp; 24: Royal Guard Set&amp;nbsp; 25: Phantom Ganon Set.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Hylian Hood's A and B are switched depending on the upper armor.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b class="SelectedElement"&gt;[ Individual Selection Ver ]&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;This version allows you to select all armors except the default one. You can also change the default hairstyle.&lt;br&gt;There are 8 bnp files packed in the zip file, so please choose one and install it.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Additional armor for NudeLink V2.0.1 [&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/mods/536202"&gt;Honey Bee Link&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;]&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;font color="#6ee16c"&gt;If you have any problems using this mod, please report them in the comments section. (We may not be able to address all of them...)&lt;/font&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;Please select one of the files below to install. Select each option in the BCML installation window.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;</description>
