ebanana.com/img/ss/mods/641630e2283d1.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/641630dde175d.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/64163239e6d95.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/641630d0b083f.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6416323ccb669.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/64163232d0e34.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6416322007081.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6416324202fd7.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/641632455d60d.jpg"/&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Update:&lt;/strong&gt; DAR 3.4b FREE&lt;br&gt;&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;CHANGELOG&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;Fixed 'Trials of the Sword'&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Fixed a bug that won't let you place the Master Sword in Korok Forest to enter 'Trials of the Sword'. When you gonna play 'Trials of the Sword', make sure to DO NOT SELECT the option 'Harder Enemies' in the OPTIONS MODULE.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;Fixed 'Play Great Plateau' Starting Option&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Fixed a bug that freeze the game when the Starting Option 'Play Great Plateau' is selected.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;Fixed Save after completing 'Divine Beasts Challenge'&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Fixed a bug that won't let you save the game after you complete a 'Divine Beast Challenge', when using 'Manual Save' enabled in Campfire Options.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Full version with more than 50 install options on&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow" href="https://www.patreon.com/DarkArmyResurrection"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Patreon Page&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Thanks for supporting this project!&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;ENJOY!!!&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;em&gt;Bugfix&lt;/em&gt;: Fixed 'Trials of the Sword'&lt;br&gt;&lt;em&gt;Bugfix&lt;/em&gt;: Fixed 'Play Great Plateau' Starting Option&lt;br&gt;&lt;em&gt;Bugfix&lt;/em&gt;: Fixed Save after completing 'Divine Beasts Challenge'&lt;br&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;&lt;b&gt;If you like this mod please consider making a &lt;a href="https://paypal.me/miirkuz" target="_blank"&gt;DONATION&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;&#13;
&lt;b&gt;Concept&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&#13;
&lt;br&gt;Something went wrong with the ritual that awakened Link, maybe Zelda &#13;
said the wrong words, who knows, the fact is that the Dark Army has been&#13;
 awakened.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&#13;
I'm Miirkuz, a mod creator for Legend of Zelda: Breath of the Wild with 3 years experience and &lt;strong&gt;Dark Army Resurrection&lt;/strong&gt; is my main project.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&#13;
With &lt;strong&gt;more than 2 years&lt;/strong&gt; of developing and &lt;strong&gt;more than 40.000 downloads&lt;/strong&gt;, DAR has become pretty popular even because some of the most important streamers have been playing with DAR for months.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&#13;
This mod add tons of unique features to the original game like a &lt;strong&gt;Skill System&lt;/strong&gt; based on collecting &lt;strong&gt;Souls&lt;/strong&gt;, &lt;strong&gt;Random Locked Chests System&lt;/strong&gt;, &lt;strong&gt;Random Spawning Enemies&lt;/strong&gt;, lots of &lt;strong&gt;Unique Weapons&lt;/strong&gt;, &lt;strong&gt;Punitive Death&lt;/strong&gt;, &lt;strong&gt;Punitive Blood Moon&lt;/strong&gt;, &lt;strong&gt;Replayable Divine Beasts&lt;/strong&gt; and many many more.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&#13;
The thing that makes this mod unique is the fact that you can &lt;strong&gt;customize&lt;/strong&gt; it using &lt;strong&gt;more than 100 options&lt;/strong&gt; and some of them are selectable in game through a &lt;strong&gt;Campfire Menu&lt;/strong&gt;!&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&#13;
Join &lt;a href="https://discord.gg/Xcrf7cSwP9" rel="nofollow" target="_blank"&gt;Dark Army Resurrection Discord Server&lt;/a&gt; to get full support, updates, beta versions, troubleshooting and more.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&#13;
This mod require a specific procedure to be installed correctly, so make sure to check &lt;a href="https://github.com/miirkuz/DarkArmyResurrection/wiki/1---Wiki-Home" target="_blank"&gt;DAR Official Wiki&lt;/a&gt; for full details.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;Versions&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Starting from version 3.0 the release method is gonna be different, there are gonna be 2 different versions.&#13;
I've decided to setup a Patreon Page for DAR.&#13;
On the &lt;a href="https://www.patreon.com/DarkArmyResurrection" target="_blank"&gt;Patreon Page&lt;/a&gt; you'll find the &lt;b&gt;DELUXE &lt;/b&gt;version. You'll find all subscription details on the Patreon Page.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;I'll keep providing a &lt;b&gt;FREE &lt;/b&gt;version on Gamebanana but it's gonna be a Single Module built with my Preset Options, you gonna have very limited install options and in game options will be disabled.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;Suggested Mods&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/b&gt;To improve the Dark Atmosphere of this mod I suggest to try&lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/mods/426534"&gt; DAR Enemies Recolor&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/mods/428063"&gt;DAR Official Reshade&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;&lt;b&gt;Discord Server&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&#13;
